tagline: Swing UI testing library for Robot Framework

SwingLibrary
============

Swing Library is a Robot Framework library for testing Java Swing
applications. The home page is located at https://github.com/robotframework/SwingLibrary/

This page is here for the keyword documentation hosting purposes only.
